                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <p>Problem Text</p>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <p>This is triggered when the elasticsearch current day index size has
                                reached the 100G limit. Post triggering this alarm, update the
                                current day index to read only mode and will remain same till the
                                end of the day. This prevents the elasticsearch filesystem getting
                                filled up and in turn prevents crashing elasticsearch service.</p>
                            <p>In this scenario no more logs are written to elasticsearch till the
                                end of the day.</p>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
